        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "THE FIR TREE",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "Out in the woods stood a nice little Fir Tree.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000002_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000002_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "But the little Fir wanted so very much to be a grown up tree.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "He did not think of the warm sun and of the fresh air; he did not care for the little cottage children that ran about and prattled when they were in the woods looking for wild strawberries.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "What a nice little fir!\" But this was what the Tree could not bear to hear.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"Oh!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "Neither the sunbeams, nor the birds, nor the red clouds which morning and evening sailed above him, gave the little Tree any pleasure.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "In winter, when the snow lay glittering on the ground, a hare would often come leaping along, and jump right over the little Tree.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "Oh, that made him so angry!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "What became of them?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "In spring, when the swallows and the storks came, the Tree asked them, \"Don't you know where they have been taken?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "Have you not met them anywhere?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"Oh, were I but old enough to fly across the sea!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "But how does the sea look in reality?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "What is it like?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"That would take a long time to explain,\" said the Stork, and with these words off he went.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"Rejoice in thy growth!\" said the Sunbeams.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "And the Wind kissed the Tree, and the Dew wept tears over him; but the Fir understood it not.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "Whither are they taken?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"We know!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "We know!\" chirped the Sparrows.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000018_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000018_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "We know whither they are taken!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000018_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000018_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "The greatest splendor and the greatest magnificence one can imagine await them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"And then?\" asked the Fir Tree, trembling in every bough.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"And then? What happens then?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"We did not see anything more: it was incomparably beautiful.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000021_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000021_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "I am now tall, and my branches spread like the others that were carried off last year!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000021_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000021_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "Yes; then something better, something still grander, will surely follow, or wherefore should they thus ornament me? Something better, something still grander must follow-but what?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000021_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000021_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "Oh, how I long, how I suffer!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000021_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000021_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "I do not know myself what is the matter with me!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"Rejoice in our presence!\" said the Air and the Sunlight.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"Rejoice in thy own fresh youth!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000023_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000023_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "He well knew that he should never see his dear old comrades, the little bushes and flowers around him, anymore; perhaps not even the birds!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000023_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000023_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "The departure was not at all agreeable.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "We don't want the others.\" Then two servants came in rich livery and carried the Fir Tree into a large and splendid drawing room.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000024_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000024_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "Oh! how the Tree quivered! What was to happen?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000024_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000024_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "The servants, as well as the young ladies, decorated it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000024_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000024_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "It was really splendid-beyond description splendid.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"This evening!\" they all said.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000025_000001",
