        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "Perhaps the sparrows will beat against the windowpanes!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000026_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000026_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "I wonder if I shall take root here, and winter and summer stand covered with ornaments!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "The candles were now lighted-what brightness!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "What splendor!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000028_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000028_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "The Tree trembled so in every bough that one of the tapers set fire to the foliage.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000028_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000028_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "It blazed up famously.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"Help!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000029_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000029_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "Help!\" cried the young ladies, and they quickly put out the fire.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "Now the Tree did not even dare tremble.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "What a state he was in!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000030_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000030_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "The older persons followed quietly; the little ones stood quite still.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"What are they about?\" thought the Tree.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"A story!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000033_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000033_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "He seated himself under it and said, \"Now we are in the shade, and the Tree can listen too.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000033_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000033_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "But I shall tell only one story.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000034_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000034_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "There was such a bawling and screaming-the Fir Tree alone was silent, and he thought to himself, \"Am I not to bawl with the rest?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "And the man told about Humpy Dumpy that tumbled down, who notwithstanding came to the throne, and at last married the princess. And the children clapped their hands, and cried.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"Oh, go on!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000035_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000035_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"Well, well!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"I won't tremble to morrow!\" thought the Fir Tree.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"I will enjoy to the full all my splendor!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "But they dragged him out of the room, and up the stairs into the loft: and here, in a dark corner, where no daylight could enter, they left him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000038_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000038_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"What's the meaning of this?\" thought the Tree.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000038_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000038_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"What am I to do here?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000038_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000038_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "What shall I hear now, I wonder?\" And he leaned against the wall lost in reverie.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"'tis now winter out of doors!\" thought the Tree.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000039_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000039_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "If it only were not so dark here, and so terribly lonely!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"Squeak!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000040_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000040_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "They snuffed about the Fir Tree, and rustled among the branches.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"It is dreadfully cold,\" said the Mouse.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000041_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000041_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"But for that, it would be delightful here, old Fir, wouldn't it?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000042_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000042_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"There's many a one considerably older than I am.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "\"Well, to be sure!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8413_284515_000045_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8413/284515/8413_284515_000045_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8413",
        "content": "How happy you must have been!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
